        "type": "stat_block",
        "subtype": "equipment",
        "text": "This ornate spyglass has a brass tube inscribed with constellations and green-tinted lens. It\u2019s often used by field astronomers to pick out greater details among stars and other celestial bodies. Like a typical spyglass, you can see eight times farther while looking through a *stargazer\u2019s spyglass.*",
